{
  "stem": "7598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no organized anti-Jewish laws at that particular point, because they were only too pleased to be victorious.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And most of these young Germans had never seen a Jew anyway, because they were, they were very, very young.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, we went into the farm, which had been deserted, and we found half-buttered slices of toast and half-eaten breakfast, which we then all sort of devoured.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite a lot of them, we sort of shared whatever we could find.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we found a little dog there licking the jam.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we just grabbed it away from him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think I had the jam, but people were just eating it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, there was no food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were in the middle of nowhere, and they were sort of--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That might have been about five or six days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But once the Germans had overrun the place, there was no point in-- well, we knew by that time or they told us and we believed that they were in Paris, and they were about to occupy the rest of France, and of course, France did capitulate.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we stayed for a couple of days in an empty house, which we just went into and slept.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we decided, at least back home we have a bed and a home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It isn't any better in France when the Germans are there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were repatriated on German trucks, because the Germans wanted order.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't want refugees all over the place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wanted them back in their hometowns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we thumb lift back on German transport of some sort.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And went back to--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went back to Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but I didn't go back to my house, because my parents weren't there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
